headline: Corrections
abstract: Corrections that appeared in print on Wednesday, Jan. 8, 2020.
lead_paragraph: Because of an editing error, a picture caption with an article on Sunday about a new rule that will allow federal agencies to disregard climate change when assessing the environmental impact of infrastructure projects misidentified a pipeline in Walsh County, N.D. While the pipeline in the photo is part of the Keystone system, it is not a part of the Keystone XL phase.
